GG_Sketchy

----------

A map made with the amazing textures by Ominn (http://www.gamebanana.com/textures/3146)

I think these are one of the best textures for Creative mappers. It has enough textures to build multiple and diffrent map types.

The map is a basic medium sized Gungame map.
It can handle up to 82 players, not really necessary. But who cares.
